#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: catalog.php
msgid "Catalog - Catalog Mode for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Catalog - Tryb katalogu dla WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: catalog.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/catalog/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/catalog/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: catalog.php
msgid ""
"Turn your store into a catalog: hide prices and/or add-to-cart, store-wide "
"or only for selected visitor roles."
msgstr ""

#. Author of the plugin
#: catalog.php
msgid "WPPoland"
msgstr "WPPoland"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: catalog.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/"

#: catalog.php:47
msgid ""
"Catalog - Catalog Mode for WooCommerce requires WooCommerce to be active."
msgstr ""
"Catalog - Tryb katalogu dla WooCommerce wymaga aktywnej wtyczki WooCommerce."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:50
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Ustawienia"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:76
msgid "Catalog Mode"
msgstr "Tryb katalogu"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:77
msgid "Catalog"
msgstr "Katalog"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:116
msgid "Turn your store into a catalog"
msgstr "Zamień swój sklep w katalog"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:118
msgid ""
"Hide prices and/or the add-to-cart button across your store, or only for "
"certain visitors (for example, show prices to logged-in wholesale customers)."
msgstr ""
"Ukryj ceny i/lub przycisk dodawania do koszyka w całym sklepie albo tylko "
"dla wybranych odwiedzających (na przykład pokazuj ceny zalogowanym klientom "
"hurtowym)."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:127
msgid "What to hide"
msgstr "Co ukryć"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:131
msgid "Enable catalog mode"
msgstr "Włącz tryb katalogu"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:135
msgid "Apply catalog mode on the storefront."
msgstr "Stosuj tryb katalogu w sklepie."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:138
msgid ""
"The master switch. When off, nothing is hidden and the catalog stylesheet is "
"not loaded — your store sells as normal."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:142
msgid "Hide the price"
msgstr "Ukryj cenę"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:142
msgid "Remove the price from catalog products."
msgstr "Usuń cenę z produktów w trybie katalogu."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:142
msgid ""
"Removes the price wherever WooCommerce would print it. Optionally show a "
"notice such as \"Contact us for pricing\" below."
msgstr ""
"Usuwa cenę wszędzie tam, gdzie wyświetlałby ją WooCommerce. Opcjonalnie "
"wyświetl poniżej komunikat, np. „Skontaktuj się z nami w sprawie ceny”."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:143
msgid "Hide add-to-cart"
msgstr "Ukryj dodawanie do koszyka"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:143
msgid "Remove the add-to-cart button and block purchasing."
msgstr "Usuń przycisk dodawania do koszyka i zablokuj zakupy."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:143
msgid ""
"Removes the add-to-cart button on product pages and listings, and prevents "
"catalog products from being purchased server-side."
msgstr ""
"Usuwa przycisk dodawania do koszyka na stronach produktów i listach oraz "
"uniemożliwia zakup produktów w trybie katalogu po stronie serwera."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:147
msgid "Price notice"
msgstr "Komunikat o cenie"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:150
msgid "e.g. Contact us for pricing"
msgstr "np. Skontaktuj się z nami w sprawie ceny"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:151
msgid ""
"Shown in place of the hidden price, styled as a small brass placard on the "
"storefront. Leave blank to show nothing. Only applies when \"Hide the "
"price\" is on."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:159
msgid "Who it applies to"
msgstr "Kogo dotyczy"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:164
msgid "Visitor rule"
msgstr "Reguła odwiedzających"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:171
msgid "Everyone"
msgstr "Wszyscy"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:172
msgid "Only logged-out visitors"
msgstr "Tylko niezalogowani odwiedzający"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:173
msgid "Only selected roles"
msgstr "Tylko wybrane role"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:174
msgid "Everyone except selected roles"
msgstr "Wszyscy z wyjątkiem wybranych ról"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:185
msgid ""
"Choose who catalog mode hides prices and buying from. Everyone applies it to "
"all visitors. Only logged-out visitors lets members see prices once they "
"sign in. The two \"selected roles\" rules use the role list below."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:187
msgid ""
"Wholesale tip: pick \"Everyone except selected roles\" and tick your "
"wholesale role so those customers still see prices and can buy, while "
"everyone else gets the catalog."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:192
msgid "Roles"
msgstr "Role"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:195
msgid "Roles the visitor rule applies to"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:205
msgid ""
"Tick the roles the rule applies to. Used only when the visitor rule is "
"\"Only selected roles\" or \"Everyone except selected roles\"."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:206
msgid ""
"Not used by the current visitor rule — choose a \"selected roles\" rule "
"above to enable it."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:256
msgid "default"
msgstr ""

